title: Mayday.Air.Crash.Investigations.S13.E09.Into.the.Eye.of.the.Stor
description:
Into the Eye of the Storm



Aired on 02/10/2014, Narrated by: Jonathan Aris



On 15 September 1989, a National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration aircraft, a Lockheed WP-3D Orion, tasked with intercepting Hurricane Hugo over the Caribbean islands is jolted by strong winds, causing an engine to catch fire and fail. The pilots of the aircraft manage to make a safe emergency landing after riding through the eye of the storm.
